WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.136
Your customers are connected twenty-four seven. They check their phone first thing in

00:00:04.186 --> 00:00:08.322
the morning, between meetings, and in the parking lot before they walk in.

00:00:08.372 --> 00:00:12.508
That means video, text, and email are not extras for you anymore —

00:00:12.558 --> 00:00:16.694
they are the everyday way Porsche owners expect to hear about their car.

00:00:16.744 --> 00:00:19.914
The upside is huge. Digital is personal. It is convenient.

00:00:19.964 --> 00:00:24.100
And it creates a record they can revisit. The risk is just as

00:00:24.150 --> 00:00:27.320
real. Anything you send can be screenshotted, forwarded, or saved.

00:00:27.370 --> 00:00:30.862
Treat every message like it might be read by your manager.
